text: Ceroplesis strandi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1935. It is known from Kenya, Malawi, Tanzania and Zambia.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis strandi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1935
title: Ceroplesis strandi
